comments: At the end of the drive, marginal contact occurs when Russell (MIN) changes direction defended by Murray (SAS).
Lyles (SAS) jumps towards Russell (MIN) during his driving shot attempt but any contact that occurs is marginal.
Beasley (MIN) momentarily places an arm around Mills' (SAS) upper body and marginal contact occurs as they engage during the pick.  Mills' reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Mills (SAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Beasley's (MIN) path and does not deliver any contact.
Rubio (MIN) legally contests Mills' (SAS) jump shot attempt.
At the end of the drive as Russell (MIN) steps away and releases from the defender, he makes marginal contact with Murray (SAS).
Murray (SAS) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Edwards (MIN) legally contests DeRozan's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Reid (MIN) places a bent arm slight away from his body and makes marginal contact with White (SAS) during the screen.
Lyles (SAS) moves A to B into Beasley (MIN) and makes body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
White (SAS) clamps Reid's (MIN) arm and restricts his ability to rebound.
Murray (SAS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Beasley's (MIN) path.
Mills (SAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Beasley's (MIN) path and does not deliver any contact.
Beasley (MIN) continues to move into DeRozan's (SAS) space and he makes lower body contact that affects his jump shot attempt.
Beasley (MIN) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Murray's (SAS) path and does not deliver any contact.
Russell (MIN) releases away from White (SAS) as the two players make contact.
White (SAS) places a hand on Russell's (MIN) front during his dribble that affects his SQBR.
Murray (SAS) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Mills (SAS) makes clean contact with the ball as he taps the rebound away from Beasley (MIN).
Poeltl (SAS) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Reid (MIN) during the rebound.
